It was great working with the @kchilites team@on the release of the Flex Era 1. Excited to announce we have partnered with @catechusa for our @canamoffroad build. Much more to come. 

These guys make super nice parts that are practical and heavy duty for the abuse we plan to throw at them. If you want to get your Canam or SXS dialed in hit me up. They have everything from billet parts and high clearance arms to full race chassis. 

#catech #catechrides #madeinamerica #quality #canam #canamx3 #sxs

🔊🔊🔊 ON! This day was a good day… Shooting with @autotopiala before we went to Saudi Arabia with the @funhaver crew to entertain for the Riyadh Global Auto Show. Crazy life off-road had taken me to and so many rad people around the world. I’m proud of the AWDTT that we built on little budget and how well it performed, just wish we were able to find the budget to run it to its potential back when there weren’t any other modern AWD TT’s #thankful 🎥 @alwaysevolving 

#horsepower #donut #formuladrift #trophytruck #awdtt #truck #tbt

#havasu #lakehavasu #howardboats #teaguecustommarine #horsepower

Swipe for a ride! … Walk around and quick #havasu rip on the 43 @magbayyachts with trip @mercuryracing @mercurymarine v12 600’s. Beautiful lines and great ride. Just need to take a rip on it in Florida water now. Thanks to the crew @magbayyachts @barretthowarth for being cool and letting us check her out. Havasu is always full of surprises. 

#magbay #magbayyachts #lakehavasu #mercuryracing

Operation front living room “Saloon Edition” is finally coming to life. From the minute I saw our house market photos online, the vision was to turn this room into our own Saloon. In the third photo we’ve got the Declaration of Independence, The Bill of Rights and the Constitution. 
Still have a few more things to put on the walls but it’s turning out so damn good. #itsavibe

Let me tell you, the vision for this house came to LIFE! 
Here’s a few more before and afters of the remodel. Still need to hang shelves in the kitchen and on the sides of the tv, add some bar stools and minor touches. But overall I’m so in love with our home and the life we’re building together in it 🤍
Check out the highlight 🏡 for the construction progress

Excited to partner with @battlebornwheels moving forward. This is a first look at their new forged UTV wheel with the correct offset so you don’t have steering issues. The forged wheel gives us the optimal strength vs weight so I can’t wait to get these on the new @canamoffroad build and beat on them! 🇺🇸

All these parts to build a @canamoffroad X3 and there is a lot more. We have a ton of great parts from @catechusa @battlebornwheels @evo_powersports @nittotire @ruggedradios @utvsource @kchilites @recaroautomotive @rcvperformance @hessmotorsports @garminmarine @gearworks_inc @switch.pros.official @sdhq and @snailmotorsports is working on the chassis and powder coat. Almost time to throw this thing together 👊🏼🇺🇸 

#kingofthehammers #canam #sxs #utv

Making progress, the @recaroautomotive Pro Racer ORV seats are finish mounted and all the @catechusa chassis parts are coated in @steelitcoatings We were lucky enough to be included in the testing for these seats along with the @funhaver team and know how much went into the safety aspect. With how many back injuries we have seen in the SXS world this was a concern and feel these provide us the best protection. 

A few more things rolling in over the next couple of weeks and we can go full steam to get this project wrapped up. 

#catech #recaro #recaromotorsport #safety #kingofthehammers #myrecaroauto #canam

This might very well make me end up inverted but had to throw a hand brake from @utvsource in the @canamoffroad @catechusa X3 for race and demo parties. Worst case it will make for a good show 🤙🏼. We also have @evo_powersports big brake kit going on the car to make sure they lock up good! We also pulled an audible and got with @rosspilgreen of @naturalstateracecraft to throw their full hydro steering on with the rest of our @hessmotorsports and @catechusa steering components. Hopefully I can beat this thing like I want to
